Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

03:46.190 --> 03:47.723
Zander, wh-what are you
doing here?

03:47.759 --> 03:49.036
Surprised to see
someone someplace

03:49.060 --> 03:50.760
they have no business being?

03:50.795 --> 03:52.695
I know the feeling
because I felt it

03:52.730 --> 03:54.397
last night
in Sheila's office.

03:54.432 --> 03:56.866
And again, I am sorry
for interrupting.

03:56.901 --> 03:59.168
But as anyone who knows me
will tell you,

03:59.203 --> 04:01.315
I take the recruitment of
our associates very seriously...

04:01.339 --> 04:03.539
Cut the bullshit.

04:03.574 --> 04:06.008
I know what you were
doing there last night.

04:06.044 --> 04:08.744
And I'm not gonna
let you keep doing it.

04:08.780 --> 04:10.279
You're pretending
to recruit students

04:10.315 --> 04:11.892
so you can spend time with her
and win her back.

04:11.916 --> 04:13.049
And it's not gonna happen.

04:13.084 --> 04:14.128
That's not
what I was doing there.

04:14.152 --> 04:14.984
Well...

04:15.019 --> 04:16.652
you sure as hell weren't there

04:16.688 --> 04:17.987
to recruit a bunch
of associates

04:18.022 --> 04:19.988
for your shitty little firm.

04:21.059 --> 04:22.425
What'd you just say
about my firm?

04:22.460 --> 04:25.861
I said I work at Skadden,
Arps, Slate, Meagher & Flom.

04:25.897 --> 04:27.630
We're better than you.

04:27.665 --> 04:28.964
I'm better than you.

04:29.000 --> 04:30.700
And you better start
accepting that.

04:30.735 --> 04:31.979
You know what, Zander?
I wasn't there

04:32.003 --> 04:33.536
last night
to get Sheila back,

04:33.571 --> 04:35.204
and you're goddamn lucky
I wasn't.

04:35.239 --> 04:37.173
Because if I wanted her back,
she'd be mine.

04:37.208 --> 04:38.841
- That's a joke.
- You're a joke.

04:38.876 --> 04:40.743
And I'll tell you
something else.

04:40.778 --> 04:43.579
My name is on my firm.

04:43.614 --> 04:46.882
I've never heard of you,
so back off,

04:46.918 --> 04:48.050
or I'll take her from you.

04:48.086 --> 04:49.685
I don't think so.

04:49.721 --> 04:51.520
Because she chose me.

04:51.556 --> 04:53.322
So get your associates from NYU

04:53.358 --> 04:54.690
or some other
shitty law school.

04:54.726 --> 04:57.393
I don't really care.

04:57.428 --> 05:00.329
But stay the hell away
from my fiancée.

